Moves a type to the heap with its [`Metadata`] stored in the heap allocation instead of on
the stack.

# Examples

```
#![feature(thin_box)]
use std::boxed::ThinBox;

let thin_slice = ThinBox::<[i32]>::new_unsize([1, 2, 3, 4]);
```

